Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:02.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:09.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like everything that's happened so far has been a trial for me to become your real mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:14.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The paralysis in your legs and your memory loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:18.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They prepared me to start everything over again from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:20.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:22.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:24.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:25.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:27.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rub it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:28.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts. It hurts, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:29.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.93,0:00:31.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:32.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:34.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your legs? Your arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:35.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My wings... hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:47.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After a while, Misuzu will begin to forget: about me and about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after having her last dream, she'll probably die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:56.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she falls asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she has a dream, she'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:01.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, you're going to the summer festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.23,0:01:03.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to the summer festival with Mommy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:06.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:08.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a baby dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean a chick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there'll be a stand selling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:14.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I buy a dinosaur?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:16.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! We'll eat some delicious things too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:19.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make tomorrow a really fun day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:22.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So please get better,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:23.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The summer festival is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:06.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.47,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Final Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:27.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they'd hold the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:38.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that gods exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did this girl do wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:46.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She waited like a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so looking forward to the summer festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't she be rewarded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:05.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'm never able to give you anything, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:08.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:11.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the baby dinosaur?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:26.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I threw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:36.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been waiting all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the dinosaur, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:50.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get it together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:55.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy will help you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a happy memory for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take good care of it and raise it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:07.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:13.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend is here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little further...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can reach our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:32.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my birthday present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:40.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to give you one all this time we've been together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but will you accept one now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes, "Gao!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:55.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't slept for a long time, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:13.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asleep just now, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Let's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:20.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sleep with you, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:26.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to sleep and dream, your pain will worsen, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:29.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't hurt for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really doesn't hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:37.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sleep a lot and get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:42.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really great, isn't it, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were doing your best,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you were rewarded, right, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:55.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't a cracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:08.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mommy, for lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:12.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you wouldn't have rested unless I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san...
