Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:19.45,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs52\frz355.585\pos(363,475)\bord1.2\c&H3D4285&}Picture Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:19.50,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs52\frz355.585\pos(363,475)\bord1.2\c&H4E68BE&}Picture Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:19.58,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs52\frz355.585\pos(363,475)\bord1.2\c&H5A8BE2&}Picture Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.54,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs52\frz355.585\pos(363,475)\bord1.2\c&H5F8DE5&}Picture Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:20.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll write in my diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:26.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:30.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does your body hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:50.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means it'll be a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:54.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, I had another dream last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You start hurting whenever you have a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hurt anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, my dreams will end today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's really nothing wrong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:10.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't hurt anywhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:12.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:18.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That freeloader said something about after your last dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess he was wrong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:26.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like living a long nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:29.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's finally over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:29.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:34.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you not to cry anymore; I'm a crybaby too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:38.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:42.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't cry when there's nothing to be sad about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:50.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream last night was about a dinosaur with wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:53.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was saying, "Gao," and flying like he really enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:54.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was flying even higher than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked back over my shoulder;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:06.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were pure white wings,\Nand I was flying through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:12.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It was a sad dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:15.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the saddest dream in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:19.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, that was my last dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on I will stay with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:25.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,forever and always.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. It's a really nice day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it feels really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells like summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of smell does it have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:40.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's also true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:53.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I don't want it to reek of my smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells a lot like you, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:02.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This summer smelled a lot like you, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of my precious mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it reeked of that, it would suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a good smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it sure is hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:28.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misuzu, do you want me to guess what you're you're thinking now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:28.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to drink juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:34.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody could've guessed that.
