Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:36.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:38.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like this one, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:46.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend the Gerurun juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
