Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gooey?! It's hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:58.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would want juice like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't throw it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to squeeze it while you drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:04.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it isn't that bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer break, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a summer break of just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:19.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's okay; we can play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:25.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to go on ahead by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:27.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:27.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Sora with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this far enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, keep standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to walk over there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because, Mommy, you're my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:53.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You and Sora are the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait as long as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:04.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:05.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, slow and steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep working hard like that, you'll definitely get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:25.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:25.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:26.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:28.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right for me to go to my goal now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:33.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:37.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, after you reach me, we'll go home and play cards or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:38.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:40.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The goal I've been trying to reach all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:48.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... did my best, so it's enough now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can rest now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been hurting all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:56.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me it's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:05.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to get better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bad dreams are supposed to be over, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:13.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to do all that I needed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:16.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll go to my goal, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:18.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:22.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:25.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we start our lives over again yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to take it back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:30.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the happy life that we should have started ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:33.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to take it back together, starting now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:36.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our happiness has just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:39.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we did everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:45.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This summer was filled with enough happiness for a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:45.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:46.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still lots of things I want to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,lots of things I want to do with my beloved Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All of that starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:58.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I would try my best one more time this summer break,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:03.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the summer break that started on the day I met Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though all sorts of things happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even though it was hard and painful sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:12.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I tried my hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:15.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because my goal was to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:18.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I wasn't all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to my goal now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just started, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:36.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:58.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally reached it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:01.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the place I've always looked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:03.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A place of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:07.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A place of... eternal happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:31.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:39.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How to escape from living alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:53.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need friends, new clothes, luxuries, or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:56.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just being with you is enough for me.
