Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live together happily at the Kamio house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:06.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:25.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've spent the days since then crying and crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:28.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've run out of tears to shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Family is amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:39.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness beyond compare and pain beyond compare, rolled into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:42.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's truly what it means for people to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I lived...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why I lived together with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:50.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were reckless and tattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:53.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,strong yet weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:56.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to make no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so much that it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:00.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You would understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:04.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're adults, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:11.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm confident now that I'm her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:17.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I might not have\Nbeen great, I'm still her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:22.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to quit my job and work at the local daycare center.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:27.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I want to live surrounded by all sorts of families.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:33.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come and visit you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:35.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The end of summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:40.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My break is ending too.
