Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown quite big.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:09.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you a different crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:15.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're Sora, I'll have to scold you, saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:21.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"What are you still doing here? She's not here anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you have to go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:27.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since you have wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:32.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is an eternally unreachable place for us humans, who have no wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:36.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you must fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:40.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For us humans who have no wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:45.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,take all of our hopes and dreams, and return them to the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:46.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:52.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll be able to live peaceful lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:59.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope someday we can meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, best of luck to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:15.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before I knew it, I was looking at the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:19.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the sky that had always been filled with a sad color,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an endless blue that continues into infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:26.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The girl returned to that eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:28.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The girl is still all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:34.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I shall continue on a journey to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:41.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And someday, I shall bring her back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to welcome a new beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(450,0)}My child,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:20:01.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The story I'm about to tell is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:05.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is the story of a long, long journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:11.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a story that will be passed down forever from parent to child, starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:15.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We continue to inherit the memories of the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:19.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We see and hear everything that happens on this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and pass them on from parent to child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:27.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The memories of the stars must be eternally happy ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:31.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the sky is clouded over by hatred and war,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:35.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this planet will be overwhelmed by grief and all will be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:40.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, the day of destruction will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:43.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is a fate that cannot be avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:51.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}may the last child, who bears the memories of the stars, have only happy memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:58.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:00.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:03.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just remembering something from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:06.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun will be setting soon, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:07.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before it does, let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check what out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:16.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing you've always wanted to check out:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:19.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,what's beyond this shoreline.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:22.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:24.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:27.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had a feeling you were thinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:31.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. I want to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:36.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go now, we can find out what lies beyond it... you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:39.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:39.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:44.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For them, cruel days await.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:47.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For us, it's the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:49.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:09.88,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(638,582)}The End
