Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:50.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruding while your master is changing is the epitome of disloyalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:51.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:57.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will not allow you to kill anyone" – was that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:01.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think I'll keep my word?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:03.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuya-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:05.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
