Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:21.55,AirInsertEng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The first one to show a genuine smile wins
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:38.14,AirInsertEng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The one I love most is smiling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:55.38,AirInsertEng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Even if I go farther away than anyone else, would you still smile for me from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:16:10.00,AirInsertEng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}When I close my eyes, I catch the scent of a summer day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:28.60,AirInsertEng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}We're playing in the river, just us two, covered in mud
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:42.71,AirInsertEng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}We're chasing the clouds; we'll find happiness once we reach them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:57.63,AirInsertEng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The first one who gets to the top of this hill wins
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:14.38,AirInsertEng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Head for the place that we love the most
